channel.title: Need help, using cheezscape source. Not a javac error! lol
channel.description:
I'm not one of the noobs with the javac error, I know too much about java to be stuck on that one, even though I know very little. What I get is this:
[img]http://img443.imageshack.us/img443/2931/untitled1xk.png[/img]
If you can't tell, it almost lets me in, then kicks me. When I try to log back in, it makes files for the username, "_". I know it's not the moreinfo thing, I figured that one out on my own. Thanks in advance for helping me out.
By the way: the last moreinfo thing was because I tried to delete the file for "_" and it obviously didn't work.
